events.name: 強く儚いものたち自動実行

parameters:
Explorer Armada: My request is now complete. Thank you for
accompanying me for such a long time.

Explorer Armada: I can't thank you enough for helping me
return Ect to her original form...

Clea: Because it was a request... No, I'm glad that we were
able to chase our dreams together.

Priestess Sophia: Before we went to help Ect, you were
about to say something to us, right?

Explorer Armada: That's right, that's right! I found this
beyond the magic circle!
Thief Nora: Wow, it's so beautiful! Is it a gem?

Mage Relm: This is something they created! I can feel
incredible magical power from it. Can I investigate it?

Explorer Armada: Ahaha, how about this as a reward? There's
an exact same thing here too.

Explorer Armada: Would you accept this as a symbol of the
bond we formed through our joys and hardships together?
Clea: Thank you very much. I will accept this as a reward.

Explorer Armada: Phoni, can you lend me your ear for a
moment?
Priestess Phoni: Huh, is it okay...!?

Explorer Armada: Ahaha, once things settle down, I'll
contact you again myself!

Explorer Armada: Clea and the others should continue to
face unimaginable difficulties from now on.

Explorer Armada: If you ever need me, please call out to
me. Just like how everyone helped me, I will definitely come
running!
Clea: Yes, please take care of me at that time!

Leader of the Chronos Thieves, Gift: It seems like they
asked us to hire them.

Clea: I handed over your subordinates to the guards before.
I thought that if I could contribute even a little to the
security of Valeria, it would be worthwhile.

Leader of the Chronos Thieves, Gift: Thanks to you, it
seems like my subordinates won't die in vain.

Leader of the Chronos Thieves, Gift: Thanks, though I doubt
you'd be happy to hear that from someone like me.

Leader of the Chronos Thieves, Gift: I abandoned my husband
and ran away, so I have no right to stay here.

Leader of the Chronos Thieves, Gift: And... adventurers who
have once again become eager to aim for it... the children
of pioneers.
Clea: We might meet somewhere someday, you know.
実績 探検家アルマダ、終わりなき夢
